        "@value": "Lose yourself in ‘The Songs from every Album Tour’ in 2026!  \n\nFeaturing songs from every one of Pink Floyd’s 15 studio album legacy.  \n\nWith extraordinary accuracy and a stunning light show - you’ll hear the songs you love, no matter which era of Pink Floyd you prefer. \n\nPerformed by top-flight musicians the UK Pink Floyd Experience is two hours of incredible music and a faithful celebration of the UK’s most visionary rock band.  "
