        "@value": "Sing Pitch Perfect with Deke Sharon & Splush"
      }
    ],
    "https://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "From the Music Director of the three blockbuster ‘Pitch Perfect’ films! With Deke Sharon's expert guidance, you’ll soon be crushing it with fellow Pitch Perfect fans. Sheet music will be provided for every audience member to join in! All ages and singing levels - and even non-singers welcome. Special performance by Splüsh, the SING! Canadian A Cappella 2025 double champions."
      }
    ],
