        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Sophie is turning 29 and we’re celebrating! This riotous, high-energy party blends jaw-dropping circus, outrageous comedy and unapologetic ’90s nostalgia into one unforgettable night. Featuring world-class performers from Cirque du Soleil, La Clique, and The 7 Fingers, this explosive show delivers breathtaking acrobatics, surprise twists and a throwback soundtrack that feels like the ultimate house party. The kicker? Each night, one lucky audience member is chosen to become Sophie — because tonight, it really is your party.  "
