    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "It goes like this: millions of records, a couple dozen hits, a Juno Award for Band of the Year, and ongoing sold-out shows across Canada. Universal Music acknowledges them as \"one of Canada's top five selling bands of all time\" and the Vancouver Sun has called them \"Canadian rock heroes of the first order ... the best performing band in Canada\". In 2023 they were inducted into both the Canadian Music Hall of Fame and Canada's Walk of Fame. \n\nThen, as now, what makes Trooper what they are is great performances and great pop songwriting. "
