        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "From the stars of the hit sketch comedy show Middle Raged, comes a hilarious holiday twist on the show that’s garnered rave reviews from coast to coast! A Very Merry Middle Raged stars Geri Hall (22 Minutes) and Gary Pearson (Corner Gas, MadTV), and features a blend of the duo’s greatest hits, PLUS a hilarious pile of brand new sketches and song parodies that skewer the holiday experience from first frost to New Year’s day regrets !"
