        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The annual Road Show delivers the very best in stand-up comedy straight to Kingston Grand, featuring an all-star lineup of standout performers. Packed with sharp wit and laugh-out-loud moments, this is a night of comedy you won’t want to miss. Warning: Live comedy performances may contain adult content, patron discretion is advised."
